        "required": true,
        "note_cn": "未控制糖尿病（HbA1c>7%）显著降低SRP疗效并增加感染风险；需内科医师协作控制血糖（Tonetti 2018 Grade C修饰因子）",
        "note_en": "Uncontrolled diabetes (HbA1c >7%) significantly impairs SRP outcomes and increases infection risk; coordinate with physician for glycaemic optimisation (Tonetti 2018 Grade C modifier)",
