        "required": true,
        "note_cn": "AI和DI为遗传性疾病，可能累及全口牙齿；MIH为后天发育性，主要影响第一磨牙和切牙",
        "note_en": "AI and DI are hereditary conditions affecting all teeth; MIH is a developmental condition predominantly affecting first molars and incisors",
