        "rule": "discoloration_type=non_vital_single_tooth",
        "treat_en": "Internal (intracoronal) bleaching: sodium perborate + distilled water (Fuss technique) or 35% hydrogen peroxide barrier technique; place base over gutta-percha to 1 mm above CEJ to prevent cervical resorption; review at 1 week; repeat up to 3 cycles; if bleaching insufficient — composite veneer or full ceramic crown",
        "treat_cn": "内漂白（冠内漂白）：过硼酸钠+蒸馏水（Fuss技术）或35%过氧化氢垫底技术；在釉牙骨质界以上1 mm处放置垫底材料以防颈部吸收；1周后复查；最多重复3个周期；漂白效果不足者行复合树脂贴面或全瓷冠",
        "line": "first_line",
        "note_en": "Internal bleaching is highly effective for single non-vital teeth. The critical safety measure is placing a barrier at the CEJ level to prevent hydrogen peroxide from diffusing into the cervical dentinal tubules and causing external cervical root resorption.",
        "note_cn": "内漂白对单颗非活髓牙非常有效。关键安全措施是在釉牙骨质界水平放置垫底材料，防止过氧化氢扩散进入颈部牙本质小管，从而导致外部颈部根吸收。",
        "icd": "K00.3, K04.1"
