        "line": "first_line",
        "note_en": "Histopathological examination of all odontogenic cyst tissue is mandatory. Dentigerous cysts can harbour ameloblastoma within their lining — clinical and radiographic appearance alone cannot reliably exclude this.",
        "note_cn": "所有牙源性囊肿组织的组织病理检查是强制性的。含牙囊肿衬里内可能存在成釉细胞瘤——单凭临床和影像学表现无法可靠排除这一诊断。",
