        "treat_en": "Implant-supported crown: single implant + healing abutment; bone: minimum 1 mm of bone on all implant surfaces; implant placement surgery → 3–6 month osseointegration → impression → crown delivery; CBCT for treatment planning; avoid implant placement in active smokers without cessation counseling",
        "treat_cn": "种植体支持单冠：单颗种植体+愈合基台；骨量：种植体各面至少1 mm骨壁；种植手术→3–6个月骨整合→印模→冠修复；CBCT辅助治疗设计；在未进行戒烟咨询的情况下避免对活动吸烟者放置种植体",
        "line": "first_line",
